ng in mind that it needs to be a space that looks contemporary as they grow.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001235\/corner-bunk-beds-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Corner bunk beds with storage in vibrant colours\" class=\"wp-image-45860\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001235\/corner-bunk-beds-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001235\/corner-bunk-beds-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001235\/corner-bunk-beds-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001235\/corner-bunk-beds-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add vibrant colours to this modern yet minimalist bunk bed storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kid&#8217;s Bunk Beds with Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Considerable planning, imagination, and inventiveness are required to get your child&#8217;s room just right, like these <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/bunk-bed-designs-for-kids\/\">kid&#8217;s bunk beds<\/a> with storage. It was intended to clear the space, giving your kids the room to play.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001228\/kid_s-bunk-beds-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Kid's bunk beds with storage to host play dates\" class=\"wp-image-45859\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001228\/kid_s-bunk-beds-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001228\/kid_s-bunk-beds-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001228\/kid_s-bunk-beds-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001228\/kid_s-bunk-beds-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make it as colourful as possible; your kids would love to host their friends for play dates.\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Metal Bunk Bed with Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want a bunk bed design that grows with your child and can be used in a guest room? Check this out! This bunk bed with storage design aims to achieve a sleek and modern look. It is why the design is simple and minimalistic. To create a pop of interest, use geometric forms in the bedding or d\u00e9cor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001222\/metal-bunk-bed-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Metal bunk bed design with storage that grows with your child\" class=\"wp-image-45858\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001222\/metal-bunk-bed-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001222\/metal-bunk-bed-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001222\/metal-bunk-bed-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/27001222\/metal-bunk-bed-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width